        public static long parseGMTToMillis(String gmtTime)
                             throws ParseException
        Parsing the TimeZone of time in milliseconds.
        参数:
        gmtTime - GRM Time, Format such as: "EEE, dd MMM y HH:mm:ss \'GMT\'".
        返回:
        The number of milliseconds from 1970.1.1.
        抛出:
        ParseException - if an error occurs during parsing.
